{"tid":33031,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[PlugDJ][排隊播]有無人入黎轉播歌? 中文音樂台","createTime":"2016-12-10T14:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T17:07:28.000Z","uid":54528,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e59227276941c5761e030bbf9238ff9a0384f209","tid":33031,"uid":54528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T14:21:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ctrlv.in/img/14/08/31/54034917a754f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ctrlv.in%2Fimg%2F14%2F08%2F31%2F54034917a754f.png&h=529470e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣東話, 國語, 普通話歌為主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新網<br />\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;<a href=\"http://plug.dj/hkgoldenmusic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplug.dj%2Fhkgoldenmusic&d=lYTXLzsLZtpcSBTv5cf0w5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=690b39fa\" target=\"_blank\">http://plug.dj/hkgoldenmusic</a>&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔識播歌可以係chatroom問/留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n詳細播歌做DJ教學 (唔點歌只聽歌都得)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cB-OOtFOhZg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcB-OOtFOhZg&d=lYTXLzsLZtpcSBTv5cf0w5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=9543cb61\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cB-OOtFOhZg</a><br />\n<br />\n呢到咩風格咩歌手既華語歌曲都會有人播 ! 冇既話 可能就係差你一個 !<br />\n<br />\n以下係介紹<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1） 打咩字句先會有表情出?<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.emoji-cheat-sheet.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.emoji-cheat-sheet.com%2F&d=lYTXLzsLZtpcSBTv5cf0w5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=a802bc5d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.emoji-cheat-sheet.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2） 禁左Join wait list之後未到我既? 其實要等幾耐架?<br />\n<br />\n睇右上角就睇到你排第幾，例如你依家係2/10，<br />\n<br />\n咁你等當前呢前首完左，就會到1/10，之後下個就到你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ctrlv.in/img/14/08/31/54034be8650d8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ctrlv.in%2Fimg%2F14%2F08%2F31%2F54034be8650d8.png&h=df76c21c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3） 仆街!點解播播下會突然去左下個既???<br />\n<br />\n可能係因為你播&amp;#22021;歌太多負皮(Meh)，當負皮數達到房間人數 1/5 就會自動skip<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ctrlv.in/img/14/08/31/54034d394d0e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ctrlv.in%2Fimg%2F14%2F08%2F31%2F54034d394d0e5.png&h=26a6d2a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4） 我想播外文歌(J/K POP, 英文歌...等等)喎，得唔得架?<br />\n<br />\n係中文音樂台就緊係播中文歌啦，播外語歌俾人Skip是常識吧，所以我地會係你播第一次個時提醒你轉翻播中文歌，第二次之後....你懂的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每個DJ每次只可以播一首，完左就到下位，嚴禁惡意負皮<br />\n開分身排隊＝死偶像"},{"pid":"887e61eb312e5ce2b216b60bc72555cd7ea6f0d0","tid":33031,"uid":54528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T14:22:03.000Z","msg":"每月8號 為紀念 亞洲天后級歌姬 王菲 生日 已被定為台殤日 由 2014年11月8日起<br />\n<br />\nRULES<br />\n1. Be respectful, don't disrupt the chat. Keep it open to everyone (so keep it Chinese and English).<br />\n2. Only Chinese songs are allowed<br />\nFailure to obey the rules will lead to you being permanently and immediately banned from this room.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n*****注意*****<br />\n深夜插播時段:自已最後一首Last想訓可以留言，工作人員會俾佢插播到最前<br />\n<br />\n為免延長排隊時間，歌曲長度限時7分鐘內　<br />\n<br />\n每個DJ每次只可以播一首，完左就到下位，嚴禁惡意負皮<br />\n<br />\n大家入黎隨便傾計，無小圈子，乜鬼都傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&gt;&gt;&gt;<a href=\"https://plug.dj/hkgoldenmusic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplug.dj%2Fhkgoldenmusic&d=lYTXLzsLZtpcSBTv5cf0w5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=db76c574\" target=\"_blank\">https://plug.dj/hkgoldenmusic</a>&lt;&lt;&lt;"},{"pid":"56ebce00786050ad0c0ec15c47dd637c685404ef","tid":33031,"uid":54528,"like":0,"dislik